item.title: How to sell things to the shop in dev 2.7? [UPDATED]
item.dc:creator: @Tatemo Tatemo
item.description:
@Tatemo wrote:

You go to your first click object packet you add the object Id and Coords then you put:

case objectID:
if (objectXz == objectX && objectYz == objectY) {
teleportToX = coords;
teleportToY = coords;
heightLevel = 0;
}
break;
